{"about_the_game":"Take on the role of an innocent, defenseless man in this horror survival game and experience frightening evil like you've never experienced before: <br>You are invited to the funeral of an unknown &quot;friend&quot;, but you never arrive. Instead, your path leads straight to a gloomy mansion where scary and gruesome things are going on. A creepy life and death adventure begins that will take you to dark cellars, prisons and even worse places...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[/h2]<br>There are multiple endings! You decide how it ends when you play!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>features:</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You are mercilessly exposed to sheer horror, the only option for you is to run and hide!<br></li><li> Hide and Sneak: Ducking, sneaking quietly and finding good hiding places is one of the main elements in this game!<br></li><li> Quick Time Events: Decide as fast as you would have to in real life!<br></li><li> Chase: Sometimes the only thing that helps is to run away and even then you have to be able to make the right decisions quickly!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>warning:</u></strong></h2>&quot;The Gravehouse&quot; contains intense violence and gore!<br><br><strong>Small bug:</strong><br>The GPS in the intro sequence sometimes doesn't load and stays off. (not bad).<br><br>F11 = FULLSCREEN!</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1673022369","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183730/page.bg.jpg?t=1673022369","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183730/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1673022369","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183730/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1673022369","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{